description: Seattle Biscuit Company is a fantastic biscuit truck on the streets of Seattle. Using only local Washington-Oregon ingredients, they're building biscuits without boundaries. Offering older flavor combos, like jalapeño blackberry jelly and bacon, and new ideas to satisfy the fusion-friendly west coast, like ham, bacon, Beechers cheese, sweet onion mustard, pickles, and apple butter, this fare has something to offer everyone. Find it on the streets and grab yourself a bite!
name: Seattle Biscuit Company
